title: DRAFT TO FINAL REPORT
description: Short-Term Endpoints Using Test (D14 and D15) and Reference Cigarettes

revisions.description: Revisions have been made in response to Sponsor's letter of May 15, 1984. See attached.
revisions.item9: No additional comment is necessary in the text regarding levels of GGrp since a valid assay may reflect levels of 3-4 lu/l or lower. However, Tables Ccin6 and Cch43 have been revised to indicate low levels of activity were detected rather than lack of sufficient data. Therefore the footnote has been changed to read 'extremely low levels of activity, including no reactivity.'

revisions.description: "Microbiological Associates" has been changed to "Microbiological Associates Inc." throughout the report.
Date line has been added to the title page.
"Final Report" and the study number have been added to the upper right corner of each page.
